ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectComing into force of the Constitution of the Universal Postal Union, the General Regulations of the Universal Postal Union, the Universal Postal Convention and the Final Protocol to the Universal Postal Convention
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the CONSTITUTION OF THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL UNION, THE GENERAL REGULATIONS OF THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL UNION, THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL CONVENTION AND THE FINAL PROTOCOL TO THE UNIVERSAL POSTAL CONVENTION, adopted at Istanbul on October 6, 2016.
